properties.areaDesc: Waters from Mexico Beach to Apalachicola FL from 20 to 60 NM; Waters from Suwannee River to Apalachicola FL from 20 to 60 NM; Waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Mexico Beach from 20 to 60 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 16 at 12:53PM EST until January 18 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds 20 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas 6
to 9 feet expected.

* WHERE...Offshore Gulf waters from the Walton-Okaloosa County
line to the Ochlockonee River from 20 to 60 nautical miles out.

* WHEN...From 1 AM EST /midnight CST/ Friday to 1 PM EST /noon
CST/ Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 AM EST /MIDNIGHT CST/ FRIDAY TO 1 PM EST /NOON CST/ SATURDAY
